PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#>
PREFIX wdt: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/direct/>
PREFIX wd: <http://www.wikidata.org/entity/>
SELECT DISTINCT ?movement ?movementLabel WHERE {
  wd:Q5593 wdt:P135 ?movement .
  ?movement rdfs:label ?movementLabel .
  FILTER ( LANG( ?movementLabel ) = "en" )
}

PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#>
PREFIX wdt: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/direct/>
PREFIX wd: <http://www.wikidata.org/entity/>
SELECT ?placeOfBirthLabel ?placeOfEducationLabel WHERE {
  wd:Q1744 wdt:P19 ?placeOfBirth .
  wd:Q1744 wdt:P69 ?placeOfEducation .
  ?placeOfBirth rdfs:label ?placeOfBirthLabel
  FILTER ( LANG( ?placeOfBirthLabel ) = "en" ) .
  ?placeOfEducation rdfs:label ?placeOfEducationLabel FILTER ( LANG( ?placeOfEducationLabel ) = "en" )
}

PREFIX ps: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/statement/>
PREFIX p: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/>
PREFIX wd: <http://www.wikidata.org/entity/>
PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#>
PREFIX pq: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/qualifier/>
SELECT ?actor ?actorLabel WHERE {
  wd:Q3577037 p:P161 ?castStatement .
  ?castStatement ps:P161 ?actor .
  ?castStatement pq:P453 wd:Q3036775 .
  OPTIONAL {
    ?actor rdfs:label ?actorLabel .
    FILTER ( LANG( ?actorLabel ) = "en" )
  }
}

PREFIX ps: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/statement/>
PREFIX p: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/>
PREFIX wd: <http://www.wikidata.org/entity/>
PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#>
PREFIX pq: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/qualifier/>
PREFIX xsd: <http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#>
SELECT ?coach ?coachLabel WHERE {
  wd:Q330120 p:P286 ?statement .
  ?statement ps:P286 ?coach .
  ?statement pq:P580 ?start .
  OPTIONAL {
    ?statement pq:P582 ?end
  }
  FILTER ( ?start <= "2013-12-31" ^^ xsd:date && ( ! BOUND( ?end ) || ?end >= "2013-01-01" ^^ xsd:date ) ) ?coach rdfs:label ?coachLabel FILTER ( LANG( ?coachLabel ) = "en" )
}
LIMIT 10

PREFIX ps: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/statement/>
PREFIX p: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/>
PREFIX wd: <http://www.wikidata.org/entity/>
PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#>
PREFIX pq: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/qualifier/>
SELECT ?vicePresident ?vicePresidentLabel WHERE {
  wd:Q1124 p:P39 ?presidentStatement .
  ?presidentStatement ps:P39 wd:Q11696 .
  ?presidentStatement pq:P580 ?presidentStartTime .
  ?presidentStatement pq:P582 ?presidentEndTime .
  ?vicePresident p:P39 ?vpStatement .
  ?vpStatement ps:P39 wd:Q11699 .
  ?vpStatement pq:P580 ?vpStartTime .
  ?vpStatement pq:P582 ?vpEndTime .
  FILTER ( ?vpStartTime <= ?presidentEndTime && ?vpEndTime >= ?presidentStartTime ) OPTIONAL {
    ?vicePresident rdfs:label ?vicePresidentLabel FILTER ( LANG( ?vicePresidentLabel ) = "en" )
  }
}
LIMIT 1

PREFIX p: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/>
PREFIX ps: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/statement/>
PREFIX pq: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/qualifier/>
PREFIX wd: <http://www.wikidata.org/entity/>
SELECT ( MAX( ?year ) AS ?lastWinYear ) WHERE {
  wd:Q203008 p:P166 ?statement .

  BIND( YEAR( ?date ) AS ?year )
}

PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#>
PREFIX wdt: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/direct/>
PREFIX wd: <http://www.wikidata.org/entity/>
SELECT ?religion ?religionLabel ( COUNT( ?person ) AS ?count ) WHERE {
  ?person wdt:P27 wd:Q801 ; wdt:P140 ?religion .
  ?religion rdfs:label ?religionLabel
  FILTER ( LANG( ?religionLabel ) = "en" )
}
GROUP BY ?religion ?religionLabel
ORDER BY DESC ( ?count )
LIMIT 1

PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#>
PREFIX wdt: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/direct/>
PREFIX wd: <http://www.wikidata.org/entity/>
SELECT ?childhoodHome ?childhoodHomeLabel ?location ?locationLabel WHERE {
  wd:Q207 wdt:P551 ?childhoodHome .
  ?childhoodHome rdfs:label ?childhoodHomeLabel
  FILTER ( LANG( ?childhoodHomeLabel ) = "en" ) .
  OPTIONAL {
    ?childhoodHome wdt:P131 ?location .
    ?location rdfs:label ?locationLabel
    FILTER ( LANG( ?locationLabel ) = "en" )
  }
  FILTER ( CONTAINS( LCASE( ?childhoodHomeLabel ) , "childhood home" ) )
}

PREFIX p: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/>

PREFIX xsd: <http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#>
SELECT DISTINCT ?person ?personLabel ?start ?end WHERE {
  ?person p:P39 ?statement .
  ?statement ps:P39 wd:Q844587 .
  ?statement pq:P580 ?start .
  OPTIONAL {
    ?statement pq:P582 ?end .
  }
  FILTER ( ?start <= "2011-12-31T23:59:59Z" ^^ xsd:dateTime && ( ! BOUND( ?end ) || ?end >= "2011-01-01T00:00:00Z" ^^ xsd:dateTime ) ) ?person wdt:P31 wd:Q5 .
  OPTIONAL {
    ?person rdfs:label ?personLabel FILTER ( LANG( ?personLabel ) = "en" )
  }
}
ORDER BY ?start
LIMIT 10
